# Data Services

- API calls belong in `src/common/libs/services`; components should call service functions, not axios directly.
- Use `@/common/libs/axiosInstance`; do not create extra axios clients or use `fetch` for app API calls.
- Endpoint paths belong in `@/common/libs/constants`.
- Service functions are plain async functions and should return `response.data`.
- Name service functions with `{verb}{Domain}Service`.
- Type request payloads and response shapes; avoid `any` in new code.
- Axios interceptor owns common error notifications; local catch blocks should log with `console.error` and release loading state.
- Use `openNotification()` for explicit success/error feedback; avoid `message.*` and raw `notification.*` in components.
